WEBVTT

1
00:00:16.578 --> 00:00:18.000
Nice place for a log cabin.

2
00:00:18.755 --> 00:00:19.977
Jake would have loved this.

3
00:00:20.044 --> 00:00:20.644
Hey, Danny...

4
00:00:21.866 --> 00:00:23.444
it's not such a bad landing site after all.

5
00:00:23.822 --> 00:00:26.088
We got the housing units right over there...

6
00:00:26.288 --> 00:00:27.866
civic complex beyond the burn.

7
00:00:28.377 --> 00:00:29.733
We've got access to fresh water.

8
00:00:30.422 --> 00:00:32.311
We might have a spot for a colony right here.

9
00:00:32.422 --> 00:00:33.288
We'll see.

10
00:00:33.555 --> 00:00:37.711
Oh, ye of little faith.

11
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:40.555
He's insufferable.

12
00:00:41.755 --> 00:00:43.199
It's worse when he's happy, right?

